layout.text: A board-certified dermatologist, Barney Kenet, MD is regarded as a master in the field of cosmetic medicine. In private practice since 1992, his roster of patients includes Academy Award winning actors and Upper East Side elite, as well as those who are simply seeking the finest level of dermatological care.
